The paper deals with image retrieval using deep ConvNets, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) as it deals with searching for relevant images. The use of deep learning models for image retrieval also falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the paper involves the use of neural networks for image processing, which falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category.
